<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Terjadi Kesalahan - {{statusCode}}</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f7f6;
            height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            margin: 0;
            color: #333;
        }
        .error-card {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 50px 40px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 400px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .error-code {
            font-size: 80px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #ef4444;
            margin: 0;
            line-height: 1;
        }
        .error-title {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #1f2937;
            margin-top: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .error-message {
            font-size: 15px;
            color: #6b7280;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }
        .btn-back {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            background-color: #3b82f6;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-size: 15px;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: background-color 0.3s;
        }
        .btn-back:hover {
            background-color: #2563eb;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="error-card">
        <h1 class="error-code">{{statusCode}}</h1>
        <div class="error-title">Oops! Ada yang salah.</div>
        <div class="error-message">
            Pesan Sistem: <strong>{{message}}</strong><br><br>
            Halaman yang Anda cari mungkin tidak tersedia atau terjadi kesalahan pada server.
        </div>
        <a href="/rooms" class="btn-back">Kembali ke Beranda</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>